"var(--o-color-2) 100%);\" class=\"text-gradient\">ເຂົ້າເຖິງປະສົບການທີ່ສົມຈິງ</font>"

#. module: theme_kea
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kea.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  Cutting-"
